1.2.0 (2021-06-07)
  o fix code and tests for compatibility with R4.x
1.1.1 (2019-10-15)
  o show total number of iterations in the verbose output for bootstrap
  o added 'facetOpts' argument to the 2d tau plot
  o added extra check for too large taus to avoid issues during model fitting  
1.1.0 (2019-06-18)
  o change the way "default" confidence intervals are calculated in case tauLog = TRUE and "discrete" tau model is used
